Comment: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.10,Main,,0,0,0,,A
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:09.32,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I should be able to meet up with\N Melone in about an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:13.24,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Ghiaccio, I'll leave the situation to you and Melone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:15.53,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,You can never be too careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.53,0:00:19.99,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I'll stay back and try to figure out\Nwhere they're headed based on their journey so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:22.04,Narrator,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Got it, Risotto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.37,0:00:26.17,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,How much longer are you going to make me wait? \NHurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:28.71,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Restoring this should be trivial for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.59,0:00:31.88,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Risotto...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:35.68,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Do you really think you can \Nget away with betraying Passione?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:38.30,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,We're running short on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.14,0:00:46.40,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Your left eye is next.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.40,0:00:48.94,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,You only need a single hand and eye to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.94,0:00:51.53,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Y-You should know better than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:55.20,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,All traitors, without exception, \Nwill be erased by the boss...{bosu kara"... I guess it could also mean that the boss will order them taken out, because it's not like he himself disposes of them. -Starfish}
